snippet.title: MUSYNX March Song Update Lineup (NSW/PS4)
snippet.description:
A brand new update arrives at MUSYNX for Consoles!

Check out the 28 brand new songs added for free in the 1.03 Update for PlayStation 4 and 1.1.3 Update for Nintendo Switch!

The update will be available tomorrow March 28!

Also, we are excited to announce that MUSYNX will arrive on Europe digitally via the Nintendo eShop tomorrow as well!

Which song did you like the most? Let us know in the comments ~ o(≧∇≦o)

*Due to hardware limitations, PS Vita update will arrive at a future date. Our apologies for the inconvenience.
